3n-giai-H%E1%BB%93-Trai-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-v%C3%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-Phan-K%C3%ADnh-Ch%E1%BB%89/poem-Z306Hwt5c8VjxS4iOHvk6g">Đinh Sửu hạ ngũ nguyệt nhị thập vãn giai Hồ Trai Phạm tiên sinh vãng Quảng Trị phỏng Phan Kính Chỉ thi hữu tịch trung tức sự - 丁丑夏五月二十晚偕胡齋范先生往廣治訪潘敬止詩友席中即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/L%E1%BA%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung/poem-SB8rSIR5Qya2_R3BWlF9wQ">Lạng Sơn đạo trung - 諒山道中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u/L%C3%A2m-chung-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-6/poem-27Te4hw0Rr99f1GFI3LA-g">Lâm chung thi kỳ 6 - 臨終詩其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u/author-kQiioNPMMw9jg3d9jImRlw">Trương Hồng Kiều</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/La-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/%C3%94n-Tuy%E1%BB%81n/poem-ftq1E6uhvXWxOU68cMcwnA">Ôn Tuyền - 溫泉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/La-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-2At56aS2QnIC1468ghv69Q">La Nghiệp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Ti%E1%BB%83u-t%C3%ACnh-ph%C3%A1t-tr%E1%BA%A1o/poem-gI-s3wrKUj2UaGg5ysuXsw">Tiểu tình phát trạo - 小晴發棹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%BAc-Hi%E1%BB%83n/Xu%C3%A2n-c%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-TsPPfpqh6-nK1xv0NVFSLQ">Xuân cảm hoài nhật - 春感懷日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%BAc-Hi%E1%BB%83n/author-0dICexiLw5Ys5jcOU7Zy0g">Lê Thúc Hiển</a>)<br></div>	</div>
